{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id0cdb42aa-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1067a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1067a"},"text":"§ 1067a.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Purpose; authority","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0cdb42ab-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1067a/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Congressional declaration of purpose","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"It is the purpose of this subpart to continue the authority of the Department to operate the Minority Institutions Science Improvement Program created under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1862/a/1"},"text":"section 1862(a)(1) of title 42","children":[],"tail":" and transferred to the Department by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s3444/a/1"},"text":"section 3444(a)(1) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0cdb42ac-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1067a/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Grant authority","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall, in accordance with the provisions of this subpart, carry out a program of making grants to institutions of higher education that are designed to effect long-range improvement in science and engineering education at predominantly minority institutions and to increase the participation of underrepresented ethnic minorities, particularly minority women, in scientific and technological careers.","children